Class StructuralModules

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.model.component.Component
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.model.component.StructuralModules
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class StructuralModules extends Component
Represents a structural module component, extending the Component class. This class is used to define the basic properties of a structural module in the system.
